snippet.textDisplay: Zach you reminded me a professor that I had. His way of teaching was sooo effective because he love what he do. I can tell that even when some of those terms are complicated and hard to simplify, you did a fantastic job describing it and the images help visual learners like me. I love science and this is my fix for the day! God bless you and your team. Keep it up!
